snippet.title: Roblox Family Airplane Travel Routine & Vacation Roleplay - Titi & Goldie
snippet.description:
Roblox Family Roleplay with Titi & Goldie.  I'm taking my daughter Goldie on an unforgettable surprise vacation in the popular Roblox game, Berry Avenue.

In this exciting family roleplay video, we start our adventure by boarding an airplane to our dream destination - Paris! Get ready to join us as we check out our awesome hotel, explore the luxurious room  and get stylish with fabulous outfits to fit the Paris vibe. Watch us tour the beautiful city of Paris and Of course, we'll be snapping tons of berrygram photos along the way.

Don't miss out on this fun-filled journey full of laughter, surprises, and precious moments. Hit that like button, subscribe for more awesome Roblox adventures, and let us know in the comments if you've ever been to Paris or where we should go next!
